		<span class="csB9803513">&sect;9-4B-7. Effective date.</span></h4>
	<p class="cs53FB8D75"><span class="csEF05ACC">&nbsp;</span></p><p class="cs53FB8D75"><span class="csEF05ACC">The physician provider fee schedule, as adopted by the single state agency </span><span class="cs68EFC440">through recommendations by the board</span><span class="csEF05ACC">, becomes effective on January 1, 1992.</span></p><h2 class="cs89687900">
		<span class="cs7A33E2F1">ARTICLE 4C. HEALTH CARE PROVIDER MEDICAID ENHANCEMENT ACT.</span></h2>
